        <div class="section" id="overview">
            <div class="section-num">01</div>
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>JerseyGarage ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy
                explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our website and
                services.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">We do not sell your personal data to third parties. Your information is used
                solely to provide and improve our services.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="collect">
            <div class="section-num">02</div>
            <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect the following categories of information:</p>
            <table class="data-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>Examples</th>
                        <th>How Collected</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Identity</strong></td>
                        <td>Name, email, phone number</td>
                        <td>Registration / Checkout</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Address</strong></td>
                        <td>Delivery addresses, city, pincode</td>
                        <td>Order placement</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Payment</strong></td>
                        <td>Transaction ID, payment method type</td>
                        <td>Razorpay (encrypted)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Order History</strong></td>
                        <td>Products purchased, order status</td>
                        <td>Automatically</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Device / Usage</strong></td>
                        <td>IP address, browser type, pages visited</td>
                        <td>Cookies / analytics</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Profile</strong></td>
                        <td>Avatar image, preferences</td>
                        <td>User-provided</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>We do <strong>not</strong> store full card numbers or CVV details. All payment data is handled by
                Razorpay under PCI-DSS compliance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="how-we-use">
            <div class="section-num">03</div>
            <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
            <p>Your information is used to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
                <li>Send order confirmations, shipping updates, and receipts</li>
                <li>Manage your account, wallet, and returns</li>
                <li>Improve our platform, detect fraud, and fix bugs</li>
                <li>Send promotional emails (only with your consent)</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="sharing">
            <div class="section-num">04</div>
            <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We share your data only as necessary:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Shipping partners</strong> — to deliver your orders (name, address, phone)</li>
                <li><strong>Razorpay</strong> — to process payments securely</li>
                <li><strong>Cloudinary</strong> — to host your profile images</li>
                <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> — when required by law</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not share your data with advertisers or data brokers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="cookies">
            <div class="section-num">05</div>
            <h2>Cookies</h2>
            <p>We use cookies to maintain your session, remember cart items, and gather anonymous analytics. You can
                disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not function correctly.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Session cookies</strong> — keep you logged in during a visit</li>
                <li><strong>Preference cookies</strong> — remember your settings</li>
                <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — help us understand how the site is used</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="security">
            <div class="section-num">06</div>
            <h2>Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including HTTPS encryption, hashed passwords
                (bcrypt), and access controls. However, no system is 100% secure and we cannot guarantee absolute
                security.</p>
            <p>In the event of a data breach, we will notify affected users within 72 hours as required by
                applicable law.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="retention">
            <div class="section-num">07</div>
            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. You may
                request deletion of your account and associated data at any time, subject to legal retention
                requirements for financial records.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="rights">
            <div class="section-num">08</div>
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of your personal data</li>
                <li><strong>Correct</strong> — update inaccurate information via your profile</li>
                <li><strong>Delete</strong> — request removal of your account and data</li>
                <li><strong>Opt-out</strong> — unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time</li>
                <li><strong>Portability</strong> — receive your data in a structured format</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@jerseygarage.in.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="children">
            <div class="section-num">09</div>
            <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>JerseyGarage is not intended for users under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from
                minors. If we discover we have collected data from a child, we will delete it promptly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="changes-pp">
            <div class="section-num">10</div>
            <h2>Policy Changes</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. When we do, we will revise the "last updated" date at
                the top of this page and notify registered users via email for significant changes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="contact-pp">
            <div class="section-num">11</div>
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>For privacy-related queries or data requests:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> jerseygarageofficial@gmail.com<br />
                <strong>Address:</strong> JerseyGarage, Kozhikode, Kerala — 673001, India
            </p>
            <div class="highlight-box">We aim to respond to all privacy requests within 30 days.</div>
        </div>

